  "_comment": "Example plan for build_reel.py. Paths are resolved relative to THIS file unless absolute. Fill avatar_clip, broll_source, and the beats. crop is the b-roll source crop CW:CH:CX:CY (aspect ~= broll_top_h/canvas.w) zoomed into the content; broll_in is the in-point (seconds) of the b-roll source for that beat.",
